PREAMBLE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

ERICK is an accessibility tool built to help people with motor
disabilities, limited finger dexterity, and other physical challenges
type more easily. This license exists to ensure the project remains
freely available to the people it was designed to help, while
preventing commercial exploitation of that mission.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
